{"tid":2318441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"創立六年 站前線守護孩子","createTime":"2020-12-09T10:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T11:41:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2336469ce6f63d2e34f38a575c689e2641e5b507","tid":2318441,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:29:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/SUUO2H2ZANFKFN42VT3SOIM4NU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FSUUO2H2ZANFKFN42VT3SOIM4NU%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=0fecaef0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FSUUO2H2ZANFKFN42VT3SOIM4NU%2F&h=b5c16baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/SUUO2H2ZANFKFN42VT3SOIM4NU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n創立六年 站前線守護孩子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/poskaOm26-FPGBt07CTdThNQ-Wg=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OAVBZYFMQZGFPPY4KNGAJB2HWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FposkaOm26-FPGBt07CTdThNQ-Wg%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOAVBZYFMQZGFPPY4KNGAJB2HWM.jpg&h=91c52387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■反修例運動期間，「守護孩子」成員多次站在前線化解示威者與警方的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】好鄰舍北區教會在反送中運動中發起「守護孩子行動」聲名大噪，除在衝突現場作為緩衝外，教會亦多次為社會議題發聲，例如為馬屎埔村民被收地等事件舉行聯署，部份成員雖曾被捕但仍發起不同行動，例如擔任「旁聽師」及派發黃店飯券，以支援其他被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警指教會瞞1,800萬拘兩人  好鄰舍堂主任涉洗黑錢遭通緝 fb暗示流亡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯署反收地 關注工人待遇<br />\n<br />\n好鄰舍北區教會2014年由傳道人陳凱興創立，一直以慈善工作及致力發聲去回應社會不公，盼能一改教會予人較為冷漠的形象。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教會多次發起網上聯署，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n去年反送中運動時，教會發起「守護孩子行動」，希望到前線作為緩衝，化解示威者與警方的衝突，多名成員包括陳凱興、「絕食黃伯」陳基裘在過去一年均曾被捕。去年9月，一名守護孩子義工曾遭警員拉入後巷包圍腳踢。事後警方僅稱他們只是腳踢「黃色物體」，引起社會譁然。<br />\n<br />\n及後政府對抗爭者的清算不斷，教會發起「守護孩子旁聽師」、「青少年醫肚計劃」、「住家飯計劃」，以派發黃店飯券、八達通，並派成員法庭旁聽等行動支援被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098bf65c4e53e9409d7fa589ce03223b01472c91","tid":2318441,"uid":172443,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋真係做左好撚多野<br />\n事無大小都會出現擋係前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff23731eb65a266968cd5c62b714b7169f1e47f","tid":2318441,"uid":186782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e21983bb7cf34d3fad1d1239a17e6bb4679f01","tid":2318441,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a0e688ed5db4db4c827db69e04872b0be613f0","tid":2318441,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img